SSLEngine on
SSLProtocol -ALL +SSLv3 +TLSv1
SSLCipherSuite ALL:!ADH:RC4+RSA:+HIGH:+MEDIUM:-LOW:-SSLv2:-EXP

SSLCertificateKeyFile   <%= vardir %>/ssl/private_keys/<%= fqdn %>.pem
SSLCertificateFile      <%= vardir %>/ssl/certs/<%= fqdn %>.pem
SSLCACertificateFile    <%= vardir %>/ssl/ca/ca_crt.pem
SSLCertificateChainFile <%= vardir %>/ssl/ca/ca_crt.pem
SSLCARevocationFile     <%= vardir %>/ssl/ca/ca_crl.pem
SSLVerifyClient required
SSLVerifyDepth  1
SSLOptions +StdEnvVars

